Nivatech Delivery Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
This is the Nivatech Delivery Privacy Policy
This policy explains how Nivatech Market, a service of Nivatech, collects, uses, shares, and protects the personal information that we collect through our multi-vendor platform ("the Site", "we" or "us"). Nivatech is committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected. By using this Site, you agree to these policies.

How the Information is Collected
Information Provided by the User
You have to provide us with personal information like your name, email address, phone number, and physical address when you register on our platform. Our app may also fetch your location information if you have enabled location services on your device. This allows us to enhance your experience by offering location-specific services, such as identifying nearby vendors for product delivery.

Information Provided by Web Browser
We may collect certain information automatically when you use the Site, such as your IP address, device type, browser type, the pages you visit, and the time you spend on those pages. This information helps us understand how you use our Site and enables us to improve our services. This information will generally be anonymous data that we collect on an aggregate basis.

Payment Information
To process your payments for the services you use on the Site, you have to provide us with payment details such as credit card information or other billing information. All payment data is securely processed using modern encryption techniques.

How the Information is Used
Providing and Improving Our Services
We use the information collected to provide and improve our services, process transactions, and enhance user experience. This includes personalizing content and communications, ensuring site security, and developing new features.

Marketing and Communications
With your explicit consent, we may use your information to send newsletters, special offers, and product updates. You can opt out of these communications at any time.

Information Sharing
Third-Party Sellers
We may share your personal information with third-party sellers to process your orders and facilitate deliveries.

Service Providers
We also share information with service providers who assist in operating our platform, such as payment processors, hosting services, and technical support.

Legal Compliance

We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect our rights and safety.

Your Rights

You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information, and to withdraw consent for its processing where applicable. You can manage these settings in your account or contact us directly.

Cookies

We use cookies to improve your experience on our Site. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings. For more details, refer to our Cookie Policy.

Changes to the Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through notifications on our Site, and the revision date will be updated accordingly.

Contact Us
For questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, please contact us at:  
- Email: info@nivatech.elementfx.com  
- Address: Nivatech, 1 Ronelle Street, Haazandal, Brackenfell, 7560.

